Package: mastergrids
Title: Utility Functions for Grid Data Workflows
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
  person("Andreas", "Bender", , "andreas.bender@bdi.ox.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5628-8611")))
Description: The main functionality consists of (i) searching for GeoTiff files
  in the "mastergrids" directory (or any other directory), importing grid data
  and embedding (spatial) data sets with grid data.
